1342,IssuesEvent,2017-03-20 13:53:12+00:00,53204916,jaraco/portend,308610,jaraco,,,closed,Add explicit MIT License to source dist,[],[],1,"Hey-lo,

I'm building a version of `portend` using [`conda`](http://conda.pydata.org/) for [conda-forge](http://conda-forge.github.io/). When possible, we try to include a link to the license file in the `meta.yaml` specification for the build; doing so requires an actual license file be bundled with the dist and (usually) that said license be indexed in an explicit [`MANIFEST.in`](https://docs.python.org/2/distutils/sourcedist.html#manifest-related-options) file so that it gets included in the source distribution.

