3513,IssuesEvent,2016-02-18 10:53:57+00:00,5776030,bear/python-twitter,4955149,jeremylow,,,closed,GetFriends() rate limiting in 1.1,[],[],14,"With the change in how rate limiting works, is there any way to pull a user's entire friendlist if it's a very large list?

