I've tried setting `scope='foobar'` but I can still call the '/api/email' and '/api/address/' endpoints. I notice however, if I change the `@oauth.require_oauth('address')` `@oauth.require_oauth('email')` parameters then I get `Bearer token scope not valid. - 401` errors. 

