5247,IssuesEvent,2017-03-17 16:17:04+00:00,70798890,logandk/serverless-wsgi,100193,bbangert,,,opened,Properly handle multiple set cookies in output,[],[],0,"Due to a quirk in API Gateway, multiple set-cookie's will be dropped to a single one. Mangling the case of the set-cookie header is sufficient to pass them through though.

