7411,IssuesEvent,2016-04-27 14:46:20+00:00,6538922,jquery/jquery-migrate,157858,dmethvin,70142,jquery,reopened,jquery wrap() function triggers error “document.createDocumentFragment is not a function” on dynamic content load (when using migrate),[],[],1,"Recently I've encountered a very strange behavior of wrap() method of jquery. I have a banner system and another site which uses that system. I try to update jquery version to the latest available one of the 1x branch. But I use some old plugins and would like them working with migrate fallback.

