Personally, I would like it to represent an online flipbook catalog of our products. 

I have attached photos of a few different icons I found on Canva, that represent what I am looking for. Any of these (or variations of these) would be perfect! I found them on canva by searching for ""book icon"" and ""booklet icon"". 

Thank you so much! Keep making Font Awesome, well, **awesome**! :)
Carissa

