12205,IssuesEvent,2018-05-08 15:38:53+00:00,49976939,learningequality/kolibri,1680573,rtibbles,3926525,learningequality,closed,Content channel disappears after UPDATE,"[{'id': 447172036, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/learningequality/kolibri/labels/TASK:%20bug%20fix', 'name': 'TASK: bug fix', 'color': '72486f', 'default': False}]",[],6,"WHERE: on http://35.229.41.226/  (creds `devowner:admin123`) which runs Kolibri 0.7.2b2.dev+git-1-gdd27d31


