diamond
  stop on: unknown event [2345]
```

if I use
```
stop on runlevel [!12345]
```
it passes the check-config.


## environment

```
$ lsb_release -a
No LSB modules are available.
Distributor ID:	Ubuntu
Description:	Ubuntu 14.04.4 LTS
Release:	14.04
Codename:	trusty

$ initctl --version
initctl (upstart 1.12.1)

$ diamond --version
Diamond version 4.0.195
```",{},{}
