13691,IssuesEvent,2017-08-16 17:13:41+00:00,51040886,Azure/azure-cli,5723682,tjprescott,6844498,Azure,closed,[VM] Sets the Marketplace plan information on a virtual machine.,"[{'id': 418936879, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/Azure/azure-cli/labels/Compute', 'name': 'Compute', 'color': 'd4c5f9', 'default': False}]",[],0,"## Description
**Outline the issue here:**

PR: #4159 

We can specify plan information. 
Include this in the release for the next  version [_params.py](https://github.com/Azure/azure-cli/blob/master/src/command_modules/azure-cli-vm/azure/cli/command_modules/vm/_params.py#L221):
```python
register_cli_argument(scope, 'plan_name', help='Name of the image from the Marketplace.')
register_cli_argument(scope, 'plan_product', help='The product of the image from the Marketplace.')
register_cli_argument(scope, 'plan_publisher', help='The publisher of the image.')
```

**Usage:**

```sh
...
imageId=$(az image show --name ""$imageName"" --resource-group ""$imageResourceGroupName"" --query [id] -o tsv)
...
local planName=$(az vm show -g $resourceGroupName -n $vmName --query ""plan.name"" -o tsv)
local planProduct=$(az vm show -g $resourceGroupName -n $vmName --query ""plan.product"" -o tsv)
local planPublisher=$(az vm show -g $resourceGroupName -n $vmName --query ""plan.publisher"" -o tsv)
...
az vm create --resource-group $resourceGroupName \ 
	--name $vmName \ 
	--image $imageId \ 
	--admin-username $userName \ 
	--admin-password $defaultPassword \ 
	--authentication-type password \ 
	--plan-name $planName \  
	--plan-product $planProduct \  
	--plan-publisher $planPublisher
...
```

