14921,IssuesEvent,2015-11-17 09:00:41+00:00,26516210,letsencrypt/letsencrypt,202474,ctron,9289019,letsencrypt,opened,Site verification fails of acme-challenge file ends with newline,[],[],0,"Using the `letsencrypt-auto` command in manual mode requires to create a challenge file under `.well-known/acme-challange`.

