    'County': 'Albany',
    'FID': 0,
    'OBJECTID': 1,
    'Shape_Area': 1379924372.27,
    'Shape_Leng': 166077.834249},
    'type': 'Feature'}

    Points['features'][0]

    {'geometry': {'coordinates': [-73.423071, 43.48507299999999], 'type': 
    'Point'},
    'id': 0,
    'properties': {'County': 'Washington',
        'FID': 0,
        'LAT': 43.485073,
        'LON': -73.423071,
        'NAME': 'Whitehall',
        'NUMBER': 10,
        'STID': 'WHIT'},
    'type': 'Feature'}

#### Problem description
I am attempting to combine two external geojson files in a folium choropleth map using Jupyter Notebook. I am using Folium 0.5 and I have Arc Server 10.5 installed which is generating the services to be used in my map (both WFS).  For each of the urls, I am ending the traditional Esri path of 'https://domain/arcgis/rest/services/ServiceName/FeatureServer/#/       with

