15375,IssuesEvent,2018-07-18 20:47:25+00:00,112676803,apple/turicreate,5673251,znation,10639145,apple,opened,Test binaries should dynamically link their dependencies,"[{'id': 783171922, 'node_id': 'MDU6TGFiZWw3ODMxNzE5MjI=', 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/apple/turicreate/labels/cleanup', 'name': 'cleanup', 'color': '34c92c', 'default': False}, {'id': 962939852, 'node_id': 'MDU6TGFiZWw5NjI5Mzk4NTI=', 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/apple/turicreate/labels/testing', 'name': 'testing', 'color': 'c1ea62', 'default': False}]",[],0,"Current test binaries come out to 50+ MB, because they are statically linking (some? most? all?) their dependencies. We should be dynamically linking where possible to save on incremental build time, disk space used, etc., especially considering our actual Python package dynamically links the same thing (so it's a better test case to link the same way the Python process will).",{},{}
