15385,IssuesEvent,2018-04-09 23:04:27+00:00,112676803,apple/turicreate,17018249,nickjong,10639145,apple,opened,warning: comparison between NULL and non-pointer ('unsigned char' and NULL) [-Wnull-arithmetic],"[{'id': 886286759, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/apple/turicreate/labels/build', 'name': 'build', 'color': '4e13a5', 'default': False}]",[],0,"We cannot adopt -Werror in part because we sometimes use NULL for things other than testing against pointers, e.g.

```
