15391,IssuesEvent,2018-06-28 19:54:16+00:00,112676803,apple/turicreate,7259873,citoki,10639145,apple,opened,style_transfer.create() fails in Docker container,[],[],0,"Hi TuriCreate Team,

_I know that Docker isn't the first deployment option for TuriCreate, may someone has an idea how to get a more verbose debugging output what goes wrong_

