17764,IssuesEvent,2017-09-12 17:01:32+00:00,50646767,raiden-network/raiden,1658405,LefterisJP,19666847,raiden-network,closed,Document installation and usage,[],"[{'login': 'czepluch', 'id': 1026799, 'avatar_url': 'https://avatars1.githubusercontent.com/u/1026799?v=4', 'gravatar_id': '', 'url': 'https://api.github.com/users/czepluch', 'html_url': 'https://github.com/czepluch', 'followers_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/czepluch/followers', 'following_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/czepluch/following{/other_user}', 'gists_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/czepluch/gists{/gist_id}', 'starred_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/czepluch/starred{/owner}{/repo}', 'subscriptions_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/czepluch/subscriptions', 'organizations_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/czepluch/orgs', 'repos_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/czepluch/repos', 'events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/czepluch/events{/privacy}', 'received_events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/czepluch/received_events', 'type': 'User', 'site_admin': False}]",9,"## Problem Definition

We need updated instructions for users to install and start the client. The latest comprehensive documentation we have is from PoC-0 -- which is badly outdated by now. The documentation in https://github.com/raiden-network/raiden/blob/master/docs/Overview-And-Guide.rst covers only installation from source.

## Solution

Installation and commandline instructions should become part of the `docs` we publish. The installation instructions in https://github.com/raiden-network/raiden/blob/master/docs/Overview-And-Guide.rst should cover using the AppImage, too (once released). This ticket can act as an anchor point to collect frequent questions to be answered in the documentation.

## Tasklist

- [x] update source install instructions (https://github.com/raiden-network/raiden/pull/848)
- [x] create AppImage install instructions (https://github.com/raiden-network/raiden/pull/924/)
- [x] document system requirements (ethereum client, ethereum networks)
- [ ] document commandline flags (contract addresses, ENS entries, feature flags/commands)
- [ ] document folders for configuration and storage
- [x] create ""get started"" walkthrough for API usage (https://github.com/raiden-network/raiden/pull/721)
- [x] document describing what the Dev Preview is and what it isn't (https://github.com/raiden-network/raiden/pull/848)
- [x] tutorial for the webui (https://github.com/raiden-network/raiden/pull/876)
- [x] update README.md to show newest install instructions and link to useful documentation (https://github.com/raiden-network/raiden/pull/1005)
- [x] Remove old PoC-0 from wiki and clean up wiki
- [x] Write about the echo node or remove this part (https://github.com/raiden-network/raiden/blob/master/docs/api_walkthrough.rst#interacting-with-the-raiden-echo-node) in case we don't have it ready by Monday (https://github.com/raiden-network/raiden/pull/811)
- [x] (optional) Add something like a glossary with explanation of the different terms used in the docs (https://github.com/raiden-network/raiden/pull/998)",{},{}
