18464,IssuesEvent,2018-08-03 21:22:09+00:00,78880128,instagrambot/instabot,19162834,valentinpompa,26087671,instagrambot,opened,API CHANGE. I can’t sign any more from a new account today. ,[],[],0,"## Please follow the guide below

