18507,IssuesEvent,2017-10-04 19:10:34+00:00,71482397,Parsl/parsl,181489,yadudoc,26490185,Parsl,opened,Usage Tracking and logging,"[{'id': 676538742, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/Parsl/parsl/labels/documentation', 'name': 'documentation', 'color': '5319e7', 'default': False}, {'id': 465598056, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/Parsl/parsl/labels/enhancement', 'name': 'enhancement', 'color': '84b6eb', 'default': True}]","[{'login': 'yadudoc', 'id': 181489, 'avatar_url': 'https://avatars0.githubusercontent.com/u/181489?v=4', 'gravatar_id': '', 'url': 'https://api.github.com/users/yadudoc', 'html_url': 'https://github.com/yadudoc', 'followers_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/yadudoc/followers', 'following_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/yadudoc/following{/other_user}', 'gists_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/yadudoc/gists{/gist_id}', 'starred_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/yadudoc/starred{/owner}{/repo}', 'subscriptions_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/yadudoc/subscriptions', 'organizations_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/yadudoc/orgs', 'repos_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/yadudoc/repos', 'events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/yadudoc/events{/privacy}', 'received_events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/yadudoc/received_events', 'type': 'User', 'site_admin': False}]",0,"For reporting purposes we need to capture the following information

 - [ ] Hash of Username, hostname (ip) 
 - [ ] Hash of Parsl script (if possible)
 - [ ] Count of apps launched by DFK
 - [ ] Site IDs used
 - [ ] Total run time

A UDP packet with this info could be sent out from the Parsl script and this could be captured and logged on a server hosted on AWS.
Here are the components we'll need
